  <div class="block-3">
    <div class="inner-block">
      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Jon joined the MHRA as Chief Operating Officer in 2016, prior to which he was Financal Controller at the  Department for Work and Pensions. He has been in the civil service since he joined HMRC in 2007. Prior to joining the civil service, Jon held a number of senior Finance, IT and global programme management roles at a FTSE50 company, The BOC Group Plc, during a seventeen-year career there.</p>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_2417">
            <h1 id="chief-operating-officer">Chief Operating Officer</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Chief Operating Officer, MHRA is responsible for overseeing the <a rel="external" href="http://www.cprd.com/intro.asp">CPRD</a>, information management, HR and finance and procurement.</p>
</div>
